  "content": "### Step 5: Run tests to verify they pass\n### Step 6: Add `delete_scope` to QueryableStore trait\n\n### Step 7: Fix all compile errors from config changes\n\nUpdate all files that reference the old config fields:\n\n**`crates/corvia-kernel/src/knowledge_store.rs`** — `SurrealStore::connect` is called with `config.storage.surrealdb_*` fields that are now `Option<String>`. Add `.as_deref().unwrap_or(\"default\")` at all call sites.\n\n**`crates/corvia-cli/src/main.rs`** — Same pattern. The `connect_store` helper and all direct SurrealStore references need updating. Every `config.storage.surrealdb_url` becomes `config.storage.surrealdb_url.as_deref().unwrap_or(\"127.0.0.1:8000\")`.\n\n**`tests/integration/e2e_test.rs`** — Same pattern for test config access.\n\n\n### Step 8: Verify full workspace compiles\n\nRun: `cargo build --workspace`\nExpected: Compiles (possibly with warnings about dead code)\n",
